welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Doctor Phillips, a charming city known for its beautiful landscapes and vibrant culture. We invite you to immerse yourself in all it has to offer and make unforgettable memories during your stay here."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kissimmee Gateway Airport serves all commercial flights and provides a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Kissimmee Gateway Airport caters to private and charter flights, offering a more exclusive and personalized experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Orlando International Airport serves domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: Terminal A at Orlando International Airport serves domestic flights for various airlines.

terminals.name: Terminal B
terminals.description: Terminal B at Orlando International Airport serves international flights for various airlines.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Gilbert Field Airport handles all commercial flights and includes ticket counters, baggage claim, and security checkpoints.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Gilbert Field Airport is used for private and charter flights and includes facilities for pilots and passengers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
